## Third-Party Licenses and Attributions

This project uses several open-source libraries and tools. We acknowledge and thank the developers of these projects:

### Core Dependencies

- **FastAPI** (MIT License) - Modern, fast web framework for building APIs
- **yt-dlp** (Unlicense) - A youtube-dl fork with additional features
- **OpenAI Whisper** (MIT License) - Automatic speech recognition system
- **FFmpeg** (LGPL/GPL License) - Complete, cross-platform solution for audio/video processing

### Python Libraries

- **uvicorn** (BSD License) - Lightning-fast ASGI server
- **pydantic** (MIT License) - Data validation using Python type annotations
- **ytmusicapi** (MIT License) - Unofficial API for YouTube Music
- **python-multipart** (Apache License 2.0) - Streaming multipart parser

### Development Tools

- **pytest** (MIT License) - Testing framework
- **Docker** (Apache License 2.0) - Containerization platform

